      <problem id="fs-idm90804592">
        <para id="fs-idm83419424">What is a potential problem with a temporary tax decrease designed to increase aggregate demand if people know that it is temporary? </para></problem>
    </exercise>
  
  <exercise id="fs-idp58190320">
